lays both the state name and the dynamically selected metric value. My current focus is on the color encoding title; while I can bind it to the parameter using `alt.TitleParams(expr=\"metric\")` for full dynamism, a static \"Metric Value\" title is also a safe and clear option for now.\n\n**Testing Title Dynamism**\n\nI'm investigating the flexibility of Altair's title configuration. Specifically, I'm exploring whether dynamic titles using expressions like `alt.ExprRef(\"metric\")` are supported and how they compare to a static \"Metric Value\" title for clarity and robustness across different Altair versions.\n\n","state":"done"}}
